  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>With a large array of restaurants available in Levi, the Design Hotel is offered on a bed &amp; breakfast basis, with the option to upgrade to half board for three nights of your stay. </p>
<p>Breakfast is included and served exclusively in the Kekäle Restaurant. The restaurant specialises in serving season and organic products but of course, classic continental options will also be served.</p>
<p>If you have opted for half-board dining for <strong>three nights </strong>of your stay, evening meals will be served at the Kekäle restaurant. You will receive a set menu on three nights with a Chef's special 5-course menu on the 3rd night.</p>
<p>A Festive Feast is included for all guests arriving before Christmas, for a Christmas celebration meal with games and music. Please note that for guests staying on half-board, the Festive Feast replaces the last dinner included in the half-board option <span>or if you’re staying over Christmas the Festive Feast will take place on Boxing Day and replace your half-board dinner on this day.</span></p>]]></cateringDescription>
