  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Design Hotel Levi mixes modern and traditional Lappish style. With beautifully designed rooms and a central position in Levi, our guests may enjoy the luxury of their surroundings with all of the Levi Hotel Spa's facilities available inside the same complex. It ticks all of the boxes for a winter getaway. You're close to the ski slopes, the Resort's Spa, and a variety of restaurants, cafes, and stores. Nonetheless, Lapland's natural beauty is never far away. </p>
<p>The Design Hotel is Green Key accredited, demonstrating its commitment to environmental and sustainable development. </p>
<h2>Luxurious rooms</h2>
<p>The Design Hotel is a relatively new accommodation in Levi, the hotel is furnished to a high standard with cosy communal areas and a range of luxurious rooms.  Each room is labelled as 'Deluxe' and provides a welcome retreat after a days adventure, each room is furnished in a Lappish style yet has all the modern touches, encompassing grey pinewood, natural stones, black and copper finishes- all sourced from Finland. </p>
<h2>Art and design</h2>
<p>The Design Hotel Levi is the result of a collaboration between a number of renowned Finnish and Nordic designers, resulting in a beautifully designed hotel. The views of the surrounding mountains are combined with contemporary Nordic interior design, architecture, sculpture, light installations, and visual art. Many structural features in the rooms are decorated with large-scale photographic prints by nature photographer Kaisa Sirén. While Risto Immonen's contemporary sculptures and paintings by visual artist Hanna Kanto decorate the reception and lounge area.</p>
<h2>Soothing spa and leisure areas</h2>
<p>The Levi Spa Resort facilities feel endless with the indoor/outdoor Spa Waterworld included in your stay. The indoor waterpark is one of the best in Finland, with a range of indoor and outdoor pools, various saunas, Jacuzzis and waterslides - plus there is a children's section for the little ones.  Treat yourself to a massage or spa treatments, or keep fit in the gym and yoga studio, which can also be booked and paid for locally.</p>
<p><span>Design Hotel Levi is part of the Levi Hotel Spa Resort which offers a variety of restaurants from modern Nordic fine dining to Burger King. Located right in the heart of the Levi village, directly below the slopes of the Levi Ski Resort. The restaurants offer excellent dining options for everyone, from pizzas and burgers to local cuisine and to fine dining menus that cater to the most discerning tastes.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
